    "title": "LESSON 8: WORD ORDER (V2 RULE)",
    "header_color": "cyan",
    "pages": [
      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 1,
        "content": [
          "German has ONE CRITICAL RULE:",
          "",
          "The VERB is ALWAYS in position 2.",
          "",
          "Ich gehe heute nach Hause.",
          " 1   2     3      4     5",
          "(I go home today)",
          "",
          "Heute gehe ich nach Hause.",
          "  1     2   3    4     5",
          "(Today I go home)",
          "",
          "Notice: When \"heute\" moves to position 1,",
          "the verb STAYS in position 2, so \"ich\"",
          "moves to position 3!",
          "",
          "This \"inversion\" happens constantly in German."
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion acht"
      }
    ]
  },
